OL,3,CThe dairy farmer who fears 200 years
OL,4,Cof family farming may 'come to an end'
OL,6,FWatch our report from Marina Jenkins
OL,8,FA dairy farmer from Cornwall fears 200
OL,9,Fyears of family farming may "come to
OL,10,Fan end", following proposed changes to
OL,11,Fagricultural inheritance tax.
OL,13,FThe Dark family has farmed for nearly
OL,14,Ftwo centuries, and since 1988 they
OL,15,Fhave been based at Trudnoe Farm in
OL,16,FMullion, near Helston.
OL,18,FThe farm is currently run by Stephen
OL,19,FDark and his brother, who told ITV
OL,20,FNews he's proud of its heritage and
OL,21,Fbusiness.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
