OL,3,CThe dairy farmer who fears 200 years
OL,4,Cof family farming may 'come to an end'
OL,6,FThe farm spans 277 acres and has a
OL,7,Fherd of 235 cows. It supplies Rodda's
OL,8,Fwith cream and liquid milk, producing
OL,9,Fmore than 2.5 million litres a year.
OL,11,FIn October's budget, the government
OL,12,Fannounced that from 2026, farmers
OL,13,Fwould have to pay 20% inheritance tax
OL,14,Fon farms valued more than #1million.
OL,16,FBut Stephen says this proposed changed
OL,17,Fis unaffordable.
