OL,3,CThe dairy farmer who fears 200 years
OL,4,Cof family farming may 'come to an end'
OL,6,FStephen said: "You know if this policy
OL,7,Fis introduced as it currently stands,
OL,8,Fit's just demoralising and almost
OL,9,Fsucking the lifeblood out of the next
OL,10,Fgeneration."
OL,12,FAs his father is 94 years old, Stephen
OL,13,Fis now looking to the future and
OL,14,Fconcerned about this change could
OL,15,Fimpact their family and business.
