OL,3,CThe dairy farmer who fears 200 years
OL,4,Cof family farming may 'come to an end'
OL,6,F"I know there's been the argument that
OL,7,Ffarmers are asset rich, but the
OL,8,Freturns that we've been receiving over
OL,9,Frecent years and with costs going up,
OL,10,Fthere's not enough profit created to
OL,11,Fallow for reinvestment in the
OL,12,Fbusiness," he said.
OL,14,F"If we are then faced with a large
OL,15,Finheritance tax bill as well, it's
OL,16,Fgoing to be unaffordable, and may all
OL,17,Fcome to an end," explained Stephen.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
