OL,3,CThe dairy farmer who fears 200 years
OL,4,Cof family farming may 'come to an end'
OL,6,FOn 19 November, Stephen was one of
OL,7,F10,000 farmers who brought Westminster
OL,8,Fto a standstill in protest, urging the
OL,9,Fgovernment to backtrack on its
OL,10,Finheritance tax policy.
OL,12,FStephen said: "When the Labour
OL,13,Fgovernment came in, they said they
OL,14,Fwere hoping for small businesses to
OL,15,Fgrow and growth to be the buzzword of
OL,16,Fthis new government.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
