OL,3,CThe dairy farmer who fears 200 years
OL,4,Cof family farming may 'come to an end'
OL,6,F"But this is going to have a
OL,7,Fdevastating effect on family farms.
OL,8,FPrior to the budget, the best advice
OL,9,Fwas always for the farm and land to be
OL,10,Fhanded over on death and we're stuck
OL,11,Fin limbo at the moment."
OL,13,FThe government has maintained since
OL,14,Fthe announcement that Treasury figures
OL,15,Fshow around 500 of the wealthiest
OL,16,Flandowners will be hit by the changes
OL,17,F- and is remaining firm that the
OL,18,Fchanges will be rolled out in full.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
