OL,3,CThe dairy farmer who fears 200 years
OL,4,Cof family farming may 'come to an end'
OL,6,F"Wealthier estates and the most
OL,7,Fvaluable farms pay their fair share to
OL,8,Finvest in our schools and health
OL,9,Fservices that farmers and families in
OL,10,Frural communities rely on," the
OL,11,Fgovernment stated in November.
OL,13,FBut Stephen believes that farms have
OL,14,Falready been stretched enough in
OL,15,Frecent years, with climate change and
OL,16,Fsoaring costs. He is now concerned
OL,17,Fthis change will be a step too far.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
